{"tid":38384,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"比黑人問路，點知佢嬲左我","createTime":"2016-12-14T01:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T03:57:40.000Z","uid":660,"like":90,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e12708f9058b80cf4b23527a68d26a6dd2caa32a","tid":38384,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:33:30.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚我同女朋友係旺角食完飯，係街上面行緊，有個孭住背囊既黑人就過黎同我講：Excuse me sir， how can i get to Tsim Sha Tsui？<br />\n咁雖然我英文唔好，但係聽到尖沙咀都知佢想問咩。咁啱我係條馬路度見到有架2號巴士駛緊過黎就埋站，情急之下我唯有指住架巴士再加上我僅餘既英文技巧同佢講：呢架，呢架，GO！<br />\n點知佢聽完之後就怒睥住我，然後連巴士都唔上就走左。我當時就覺得好奇怪，但我返屋企一諗先發覺我唔應該用手指住架巴士，因為手指指呢個動作可能係黑人眼中係唔禮貌既。<br />\n所以我想提一提大家唔好係黑人面前手指指"},{"pid":"feb5605da9e31beccbfdf2f7ebf2bda0807b897a","tid":38384,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"唔錯 6.5/10"},{"pid":"a91ffb09bfbc87206c15b85071e7515c054ee00b","tid":38384,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:35:39.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"94a188a82f87b359763b7bc44c61ea037b470551","tid":38384,"uid":19667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:35:50.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的 重作"},{"pid":"aa5e692fcdd6309bdee9508b0a2d5cabd11f53d5","tid":38384,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係你"},{"pid":"efafcb64e0fe6016b62cef6841a94a0c1f985bb5","tid":38384,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇是咁的 重作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真人真事"},{"pid":"d94759794f3ae58509d925f24292833c81ccbbc6","tid":38384,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:37:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOk"},{"pid":"6bce63cf1264b07c815569a2a95e7b6ecc8817e2","tid":38384,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:39:37.000Z","msg